claim.claim-text:
A method (500) for wireless communications, comprising:
receiving (502) multiple feedback aspects of a channel for the wireless communications;
determining (504) multiple codewords (W1, W2) based on the multiple feedback aspects;
determining (506) a final precoding matrix (W) based on the multiple codewords (W1, W2);
enforcing (508) at least one codebook property in at least one of the final precoding matrix (W) or the multiple codewords (W1, W2), wherein enforcing the at least one codebook property comprises quantizing each of the multiple codewords (W1, W2) or
quantizing the final precoding matrix (W);
applying (510) the final precoding matrix (W) to a plurality of spatial streams to form precoded spatial streams; and
transmitting (512) the precoded spatial streams.

An apparatus (500A) for wireless communications, comprising:
means for receiving (502A) multiple feedback aspects of a channel for the wireless communications;
means for determining (504A) multiple codewords (W1, W2) based on the multiple feedback aspects;
means for determining (506A) a final precoding matrix (W) based on the multiple codewords (W1, W2);
means for enforcing (508A) at least one codebook property in at least one of the final precoding matrix (W) or the multiple codewords (W1, W2), wherein enforcing the at least one codebook property comprises quantizing each of the multiple codewords (W1, W2) or quantizing the final precoding matrix (W);
means for applying (510A) the final precoding matrix (W) to a plurality of spatial streams to form precoded spatial streams; and
means for transmitting (512A) the precoded spatial streams.
